nephropathy.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/118865/', '', 'Ethiodized oil, Iopanoic acid, Tyropanoic acid, Iopodic acid', '', 1767369485);
